{
  "texts": [
    "Dependent variables were entered in two blocks.",
    "The first block contained demographic characteristics: gender, age, income, education, race/ethnicity, and employment status.",
    "Other individual traits previously found to influence attitudes about technology comprised the second block: innovativeness, internal LoC, and PTC.",
    "Prior to data analysis, assumptions of multiple regression were tested.",
    "For all three models, we accepted that the residuals were normally distributed based on the standardized normal probability (P-P) plot; homogeneity of the variance of the residuals was tested and accepted by plotting the residuals against fitted values and using the Breusch-Pagan test for heteroscedasticity where p > 0.05 for all models."
  ]
}